    window, for when Viewfonts 2 is @{"iconified" link commodity}.

   Pressing any of the underlined letters will activate that gadget.
   Pressing help will activate the online help, but this Guide file
  must be in the same directory as the main program.

     The menus are shown below, then the Viewfonts 2 window.


